<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main.css"/>
</head>

<body>
<div
  class="hero h-[70vh]"
  style="background-image: url(https://ww3.rics.org/content/dam/rics/images/modus/built-environment/february-2023/baku/header_baku-cityscape_baku_modus_feb-23_SHUTTERSTOCK.jpg);background-size: cover; background-position: center;">
  <div class="hero-overlay bg-opacity-60"></div>
  <div class="hero-content text-neutral-content text-center">
    <div class="max-w-md">
      <h1 class="mb-5 text-5xl font-bold">Baku</h1>
      <p class="mb-5">
 Baku, the capital of Azerbaijan, is a vibrant city located on the western coast of the Caspian Sea. 
It blends ancient history with modern architecture, featuring landmarks like the Flame Towers and the medieval Old City (Icherisheher). 
Known for its oil-rich economy and dynamic nightlife, Baku also hosts international events such as Formula 1 races.
 The cityâ€™s seaside boulevard and unique cultural mix make it a captivating destination for travelers.
      </p>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
  <div class="flex justify-end px-8 py-6">
    <button class="bg-blue-700 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded">
      <a href="/memories/add">Add Location</a>
    </button>
  </div>
   <div class="overflow-x-auto mt-6">
  <table class="table table-zebra">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Image</th>
        <th>Name</th>
        <th>Category</th>
        <th>Address</th>
        <th>Comments</th>
        <th>Actions</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% location.forEach(loc => { %>
        <tr>
          <td><img src="<%= loc.image %>" class="w-24 h-16 object-cover" /></td>
          <td><%= loc.name %></td>
          <td><%= loc.category %></td>
          <td><%= loc.address %></td>
          <td><%= loc.comments %></td>
          <td> <a href="/memories/delete/<%=loc.id%>" class="btn btn-sm btn-error">Delete</a></td>
        </tr>
      <% }) %>
    </tbody>
  </table>

</body>

</html>